name: FUSION
description:
FUSION is a piece where I put all my knowledge, all my dedication, and all my heart into every little detail. An art where I literally fused everything I've learned in the last few years, my references, my sci-fi aesthetic and my personal touch. This piece is very important to me, it's a mark in my career as a 3D artist, and I hope you love it as much as I do. 

FUSION is the essence of PSYCR4FT project and all his aspects. 

This piece is one of my 3 entries for #BillelisRound2 contest. 

3000x3000
